ygData.msgSnippet: Hey Ray, Taren is currently in Qeynos but have SoW will travel.  Look for Gunky or Tiramisu (2 of my other characters) to be playing or tell my boyfriend
ygData.messageBody:
Hey Ray,
Taren is currently in Qeynos but have SoW will travel. Look for
Gunky or Tiramisu (2 of my other characters) to be playing or tell my
boyfriend Cabalah to tell me to get on and I'll meet you somewhere to
invite you. I am on pretty much every night (days on weekends) from 5
til about 10;11;12;1;2ish PST. Depends on the mood really. =)

Hope to see you soon,
Andy
Taren
Tiramisu
Tuttun
Gunky
Mame
Ocacious
Kuvaren
All on Rodcet Nife

Gunky recently joined a guild les'innocentes I think is the name. Just
waiting for the new evil guild to form. He was lonely in Blackburrow
and that lead him to give into peer pressure when his groupies invited
him. He has low willpower stats. Buff me plz. Gunky is also getting
pretty good at making arrows =) (told you he was lonely)
Himz iz a fletcher.
